languages.text: {n}Вайс хмурится, явно снедаемый темными подозрениями.{/n} "Меня тревожат эти недомолвки, но... Не смею спорить с Вашей Светлостью. Путь с Януса займет некоторое время, я доложу, когда госпожа Вьятт прибудет".

{n}Weisz frowns, clearly tormented by dark suspicions.{/n} "I am worried by all this reticence and omission, but... I will not presume to argue with Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The journey from Janus will take some time. I will report back when Lady Vyatt arrives."

languages.text: {n}Weisz frunce el ceño, evidentemente atormentado por una oscura sospecha.{/n} «Tantas reticencias y omisiones me preocupan, pero... no osaría discutir con mi{mf|lord|lady}. Hay una larga travesía desde Janus. Le avisaré cuando llegue lady Vyatt».

languages.text: {n}ワイズは眉をしかめ、明らかに疑う暗い気持ちに頭を悩ませている。{/n}「沈黙と言葉不足が気がかりなのですが…陛下と言い争うつもりはございません。ヤヌスからの旅には多少時間がかかるでしょう。レディ・ビャットが到着されたら、改めてご報告いたします」
languages.original_text: {n}Weisz frowns, clearly tormented by dark suspicions.{/n} "I am worried by all this reticence and omission, but... I will not presume to argue with Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The journey from Janus will take some time. I will report back when Lady Vyatt arrives."

languages.text: {n}威茨皱起眉头，脑海中显然浮现了许多阴暗的猜测。{/n}“我对这样的安排感到担忧，不过……我不敢与您争辩，大人。维亚特女士要花些时间才能从加努斯赶来，等她到了之后，我再向您汇报吧。”
languages.original_text: {n}Weisz frowns, clearly tormented by dark suspicions.{/n} "I am worried by all this reticence and omission, but... I will not presume to argue with Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The journey from Janus will take some time. I will report back when Lady Vyatt arrives."

languages.text: {n}Weisz runzelt die Stirn, als würde er von einem dunklen Verdacht gequält.{/n} "All die Verschwiegenheit und die Auslassungen bereiten mir Sorge, aber ... Ich werde mir nicht anmaßen, mit Eurer {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft} zu streiten." Die Anreise von Janus wird eine Weile dauern. Ich melde mich, sobald Lady Vyatt eintrifft."
languages.original_text: {n}Weisz frowns, clearly tormented by dark suspicions.{/n} "I am worried by all this reticence and omission, but... I will not presume to argue with Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The journey from Janus will take some time. I will report back when Lady Vyatt arrives."

languages.text: {n}Weisz se renfrogne, visiblement tourmenté par de bien sinistres soupçons.{/n} « Votre insouciance et votre entêtement ne laissent pas de m'inquiéter, mais... je ne me permettrais pas de contester votre jugement, Votre Seigneurie. La traversée depuis Janus va prendre un certain temps. Je vous préviendrai lorsque dame Vyatt sera arrivée. »
languages.original_text: {n}Weisz frowns, clearly tormented by dark suspicions.{/n} "I am worried by all this reticence and omission, but... I will not presume to argue with Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The journey from Janus will take some time. I will report back when Lady Vyatt arrives."

languages.text: {n}Weisz, karanlık kuşkuların sancısını çektiği aşikâr bir hâlde kaşlarını çatıyor.{/n} "Tüm bu sırlar ve ihmaller beni endişelendiriyor ama... {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri'yle tartışmak haddime değil. Janus'tan buraya yolculuk zaman alacaktır. Leydi Vyatt vardığı an size bildireceğim."
